    <h2 class="guide-page__title">出片攻略</h2>
    <p class="guide-page__subtitle">穿搭配色 · 修图技巧 · 爆款构图 · 短视频拍摄，让你的日本行程出片率翻倍</p>
  </div>

  <div class="guide-modules">

    {# ── 日本街拍穿搭 ── #}
    <div class="guide-module page-break-avoid">
      <div class="guide-module__header">
        <span class="guide-module__icon">👗</span>
        <h3 class="guide-module__title">日本街拍穿搭指南</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="guide-module__body">
        <div class="outfit-season-grid">

          <div class="outfit-season">
            <div class="outfit-season__title outfit-season__title--spring">🌸 春季（3-5月）</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__temp">气温 10-20°C，早晚偏凉</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__items">
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">上衣</span>
                <span>奶白/浅粉/薄荷绿针织衫或衬衫，呼应樱花色系</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">外套</span>
                <span>薄款风衣（米白/驼色）或小西装，拍照好看且实用</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">下装</span>
                <span>浅色半裙（樱花背景配白/粉裙）或浅色直筒裤</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">鞋子</span>
                <span>白色运动鞋（每天1万步必备）或奶茶色乐福鞋</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item outfit-item--tip">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">配色方案</span>
                <span>粉×白×米 = 日系甜美；白×驼×棕 = 日系简约；浅绿×白 = 清新文艺</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="outfit-season">
            <div class="outfit-season__title outfit-season__title--summer">☀️ 夏季（6-9月）</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__temp">气温 28-35°C，湿热</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__items">
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">首选</span>
                <span>棉麻连衣裙（白/浅蓝/柠檬黄），轻便透气且百搭背景</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">上衣</span>
                <span>白色宽松棉T + 浅色短裤，最简单出片</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">必备</span>
                <span>防晒外套（拍照时脱掉），护肤同时保留造型</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item outfit-item--tip">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">特别建议</span>
                <span>祇园/浅草穿浴衣（甚平）出镜！租赁店约¥2000-3000/套，配合传统建筑背景出片率极高</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="outfit-season">
            <div class="outfit-season__title outfit-season__title--autumn">🍂 秋季（10-11月）</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__temp">气温 15-25°C，最舒适</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__items">
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">色系</span>
                <span>橙/红/棕/墨绿呼应红叶，与背景融为一体</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">单品</span>
                <span>格纹外套/毛呢大衣 + 深色系打底，秋日文艺感</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">配件</span>
                <span>针织帽/贝雷帽 + 围巾，提升整体质感</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item outfit-item--tip">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">红叶背景配色</span>
                <span>深蓝×红叶=对比强烈；深绿×红叶=和谐自然；全身深色=突出景色</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="outfit-season">
            <div class="outfit-season__title outfit-season__title--winter">❄️ 冬季（12-2月）</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__temp">气温 3-12°C，干冷</div>
            <div class="outfit-season__items">
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">外套</span>
                <span>长款深色大衣（黑/深灰/深蓝），衬托清冷冬日感</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">造型</span>
                <span>高领毛衣打底，叠穿质感佳，颈部有保暖又好看</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">配件</span>
                <span>皮手套/毛绒帽 + 简约围巾，冬日清冷质感</span>
              </div>
              <div class="outfit-item outfit-item--tip">
                <span class="outfit-item__label">温泉/雪景</span>
                <span>温泉旅馆提供浴衣，雪中穿浴衣是绝美场景，把握机会拍！</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {# ── 手机修图参数 ── #}
    <div class="guide-module page-break-avoid">
      <div class="guide-module__header">
        <span class="guide-module__icon">🎨</span>
        <h3 class="guide-module__title">手机修图参数推荐</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="guide-module__body">
        <div class="editing-presets">

          <div class="editing-preset">
            <div class="editing-preset__name">🌸 日系清透风（最通用）</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__desc">适合：樱花、神社、街道、人像</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__params">
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">曝光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:60%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+0.3</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">对比度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:40%"></span></span><span class="param-value">-15</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">高光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:35%"></span></span><span class="param-value">-20</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">阴影</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:65%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+15</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">色温</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:40%"></span></span><span class="param-value">偏冷 -10</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">饱和度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:45%"></span></span><span class="param-value">-5</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="editing-preset__app">推荐使用 Lightroom Mobile 或 Snapseed</div>
          </div>

          <div class="editing-preset">
            <div class="editing-preset__name">🍂 秋日胶片风</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__desc">适合：红叶、京都小巷、傍晚街景</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__params">
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">曝光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:55%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+0.1</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">对比度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:55%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+10</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">高光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:30%"></span></span><span class="param-value">-25</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">阴影</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:60%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+10</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">色温</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:60%"></span></span><span class="param-value">偏暖 +15</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">橙色饱和度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:70%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+20</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="editing-preset__app">VSCO A4 预设效果类似，再微调色温即可</div>
          </div>

          <div class="editing-preset">
            <div class="editing-preset__name">🌃 赛博夜景风</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__desc">适合：涩谷/新宿/道顿堀夜景</div>
            <div class="editing-preset__params">
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">曝光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:50%"></span></span><span class="param-value">±0</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">对比度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:65%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+20</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">高光</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:30%"></span></span><span class="param-value">-30</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">阴影</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:55%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+5</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">饱和度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:65%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+15</span></div>
              <div class="param-row"><span class="param-name">自然饱和度</span><span class="param-bar"><span class="param-fill" style="width:60%"></span></span><span class="param-value">+10</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="editing-preset__app">拍摄时用夜间模式，修图时用 Lightroom 的 HSL 单独提升蓝色/紫色</div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {# ── 小红书爆款构图 ── #}
    <div class="guide-module page-break-avoid">
      <div class="guide-module__header">
        <span class="guide-module__icon">📱</span>
        <h3 class="guide-module__title">小红书爆款构图 5 种</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="guide-module__body">
        <div class="xiaohongshu-templates">

          <div class="xhs-template">
            <div class="xhs-template__number">01</div>
            <div class="xhs-template__content">
              <div class="xhs-template__title">走路背影 + 引导线</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__desc">主角背对镜头走进景深处（鸟居走廊/竹林/石板路），拍摄者站在引导线起点，人物在前方1/3处。<br>关键：人物别太小（约占画面1/5-1/4），走路姿势自然。</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__hashtag">#背影 #引导线 #日本街道</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="xhs-template">
            <div class="xhs-template__number">02</div>
            <div class="xhs-template__content">
              <div class="xhs-template__title">坐着仰拍 + 自然框架</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__desc">主角坐在樱花树下/竹林旁/窗边，仰角45°拍摄，自然枝叶/门框作为上方边框。<br>关键：主角视线看向远方或轻低头，避免直视镜头。</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__hashtag">#樱花写真 #日系人像 #仰拍</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="xhs-template">
            <div class="xhs-template__number">03</div>
            <div class="xhs-template__content">
              <div class="xhs-template__title">大场景人物渺小感</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__desc">主角站在壮观场景前（大鸟居/城堡/神社正门），人物仅占画面5-10%，展现建筑/自然的震撼规模。<br>关键：主角穿颜色对比强的衣服（白/红/黄），才不会消失在背景中。</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__hashtag">#大景 #空间感 #伏见稻荷</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="xhs-template">
            <div class="xhs-template__number">04</div>
            <div class="xhs-template__content">
              <div class="xhs-template__title">抬头望天 + 仰拍</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__desc">手机平放地面或极低角度（10cm），仰拍天空背景+主角。竹林/樱花/鸟居走廊都适合。<br>关键：主角不要完全居中，略偏一侧更有动感；天空要有云朵或自然元素才好看。</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__hashtag">#低角度 #仰拍天空 #竹林</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="xhs-template">
            <div class="xhs-template__number">05</div>
            <div class="xhs-template__content">
              <div class="xhs-template__title">窗户/门洞框景</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__desc">站在窗外，用房间窗框将主角和外面的景色"框"起来。咖啡馆窗边/旅馆格子窗/车站月台门洞都适用。<br>关键：背景需有清晰的景色（街道/庭园），不能是单调白墙；主角与框保持适当距离。</div>
              <div class="xhs-template__hashtag">#框景 #窗边 #日式咖啡馆</div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {# ── 短视频拍摄建议 ── #}
    <div class="guide-module page-break-avoid">
      <div class="guide-module__header">
        <span class="guide-module__icon">🎬</span>
        <h3 class="guide-module__title">短视频拍摄建议</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="guide-module__body">
        <div class="video-tips">
          <div class="video-tip-item">
            <div class="video-tip-item__title">📐 竖版还是横版？</div>
            <div class="video-tip-item__desc">小红书/抖音/Reels → 竖版（9:16）；YouTube/朋友圈 → 横版（16:9）。建议用手机竖拍，后期比横转竖好用。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="video-tip-item">
            <div class="video-tip-item__title">🎵 配乐选择</div>
            <div class="video-tip-item__desc">日系行程首选：日系轻音乐/LoFi/城市流行（如ヨルシカ、YOASOBI的舒缓版）。卡点视频：找节奏明确的电子音乐，每次镜头切换在节拍处。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="video-tip-item">
            <div class="video-tip-item__title">✂️ 10-15秒黄金剪辑节奏</div>
            <div class="video-tip-item__desc">0-3秒：开场钩子（最美的一幕/有悬念的场景）→ 3-12秒：主要内容（2-3个地点）→ 12-15秒：结尾定格（人物或美景）。避免每个镜头超过3秒。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="video-tip-item">
            <div class="video-tip-item__title">🎯 必拍的5个视频素材</div>
            <div class="video-tip-item__desc">
              ① 走路的脚步特写（石板路/散落樱花的地面）<br>
              ② 手持食物/饮品在美景前（奶茶/樱花糕 + 景色背景）<br>
              ③ 360°环景（站在景点中央慢慢转一圈）<br>
              ④ 穿越门洞/鸟居的第一人称视角<br>
              ⑤ 远景人物走进/走出画面（有出现有消失）
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="guide-page__footer">
    本攻略由 Travel AI 智能生成 · 出片效果因人而异，最重要的是享受当下
  </div>

</section>
